data.description: Welcome to your dream mountain retreat in beautiful Blue Ridge, GA! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home combines modern comfort with a mountain cabin feel. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by warm hardwood floors that run throughout the main living spaces.    The interior features a perfect blend of wood and sheetrock, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The updated mountain cabin vibe gives you the feeling of a serene escape, while still enjoying the conveniences of modern living.    The heart of this home is its gorgeous living area, with wraparound views of the serene, peaceful nature. Imagine cozy evenings by the gas fireplace or enjoying meals in the well-appointed kitchen with modern appliances (gas stove!) and ample counter space.    The main floor hosts 2 primary bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms, providing private and relaxing retreats. Upstairs, two additional bedrooms offer comfortable accommodation for family or guests.
